---
title: HelloHero: Saucy Mediterranean Beef Gnocchi with Basil Pesto & Parmesan
description: Bring the Italian restaurant vibes to your dinner table with some help from our pillowy potato gnocchi. Whip up a rich herbed tomato sauce, top with sharp Parmesan and dinner is done!
